# OGM Knowledge Base (agents)

Before **any** Olive Glass & Marble quoter-tool task (edits, uploads, debugging live files):

1. Read `/Users/tanyawhite/OGM/github-backups/ogm-workspace/docs/OGM-AGENT-WORKFLOW.md`
2. Read `/Users/tanyawhite/OGM/github-backups/ogm-workspace/docs/OGM-SITE-STRUCTURE.md`
3. Follow `.cursor/rules/ogm-edit-workflow.mdc` (fresh `start`, `finish`, explicit upload approval)

## Never use as edit source

- Mac `backups/`, Archive folders, Trash
- Stale `quoter-tool-working/` without same-session `ogm-workflow.sh start`
- `fresh-godaddy-pulls/` except the pull just created by `start`
- GoDaddy server `backups/` folder (history only)
- GitHub repo (docs/scripts only — not live site files)

## Valid edit path

`ogm-workflow.sh start` → edit `quoter-tool-working/<file>` → `finish` → ask → optional `upload`

